the fairgrounds includes the gary weikel events center ( a 4,000 square foot multi - purpose building ) ; the evergreen speedway with its paved oval track , is the only nascar venue in washington and has a 7,000-seat covered grandstand ; a clear - span sports arena that can seat 4,000 , two rv areas with dump stations , and a variety of other permanent exhibition facilities .

annual events : monroe , near snohomish in this state , is the site of the annual evergreen state fair

